{"build_type":"library","description":"Layer-1 wait/wake primitive (wake-object-eventfd-replacement-DESIGN). Blocks the CALLING thread while the 4-byte shared marker word at address `word` still equals `expected`; returns once it differs. Fast path: reads the marker in userspace and returns immediately with NO syscall if already changed. Otherwise FUTEX_WAIT (op 0) via the single host-port futex primitive, then tail-recurses to re-check (spurious wakeups, signals). The marker word lives in stable shared memory the caller owns. Lost-wakeup safety: the waker must change the marker BEFORE calling the matching release primitive; FUTEX_WAIT itself re-compares *word==expected atomically before sleeping.","module_name":"suspend-calling-thread-awaiting-shared-marker","package_name":"suspend-calling-thread-awaiting-shared-marker","function_definitions":{"suspend-calling-thread-awaiting-shared-marker":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"word","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"expected","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"op_wait","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"v","base":"word","index":"zero","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"v"},"rhs":{"value":"expected"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"v"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"operate-futex-value-across-userspace-address","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"word"},{"kind":"var","value":"op_wait"},{"kind":"var","value":"expected"}],"result_assignment_variable":"fw","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"suspend-calling-thread-awaiting-shared-marker","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"word"},{"kind":"var","value":"expected"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}]}}}